Video_Title: Dinner Lady | Lemon Tart Review ( The Best Dessert E-Juice I Ever Had )
Description:

Name: Alex
Video_Title: How to Use Nicotine (Nic) Shots - Vape School
Description:
click here to learn more about us: http://bit.ly/3bbhsv5

nicotine shots, or nic shots for short, have become a part of the vaping industry recently. the purpose of this video is to educate you on the basics of nic shots. there are some links to helpful nicotine shot calculators below to help you mix an e-liquid to your desired nicotine strength. warning: nicotine shots are highly concentrated and can result in nicotine poisoning if misused. if you have any doubts as to the strength of your nicotine shot or how best to use them, please contact the manufacturer of your nicotine shot. this video should not be the sole source of information you consult for how to use nicotine shots.
